{"pageid":332135,"pagename":"Atlas and Meridian","title":"Atlas and Meridian","displaytitle":"Atlas and Meridian","revid":14242226,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Atlas_and_Meridian.png"},{"name":"description","value":"Atlas and Meridian are the names of the two small lizard creatures that surround the minimap on the user interface in fixed screen.&#91;1&#93; Their identities were revealed in the seventh issue of Postbag from the Hedge. Atlas and Meridian, according to the Postbag, saw a job advertisement in the Varrock Herald reading, 'Amazing opportunity for 2 trustworthy beings. Be gazed upon by millions and hold the world in your claws! No previous experience required, but good sense of direction a bonus.' The reality of their job was not what they had expected."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"noexcerpt noprint nomobile navigation-not-searchable rs-external-header-links\" style=\"display:none\"><span class=\"rs-header-icon rs-header-icon-rs\" data-text=\"RuneScape\" data-title=\"The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on Atlas and Meridian.\" data-site=\"rs\">The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: <a href=\"https://runescape.wiki/w/Atlas_and_Meridian\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"rsw:Atlas and Meridian\">rsw:Atlas and Meridian</a></span></div>\n<table class=\"messagebox\">\n<tbody><tr><td style=\"width: 50px;\"><div class=\"center\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><img alt=\"Postbag from the Hedge icon.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/Postbag_from_the_Hedge_icon.jpg/40px-Postbag_from_the_Hedge_icon.jpg?650e3\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Postbag_from_the_Hedge_icon.jpg/60px-Postbag_from_the_Hedge_icon.jpg?650e3 1.5x, /images/Postbag_from_the_Hedge_icon.jpg?650e3 2x\" data-file-width=\"70\" data-file-height=\"70\" /></div></div></td>\n<td><span class=\"messagebox-title\"><b>This article contains information <i>only</i> featured in <a href=\"/w/Postbag_from_the_Hedge\" title=\"Postbag from the Hedge\">Postbag from the Hedge</a>.</b></span><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><div style=\"font-size:0.85em; line-height:1.4em;\" class=\"messagebox-text\">Postbags released during the <i><a href=\"/w/RuneScape_2\" title=\"RuneScape 2\">RuneScape 2</a></i> era (2005-07) are generally not considered canon, unless otherwise mentioned. Postbags released during the <i>Old School</i> era (since 2021) are generally considered canon.\n</div></td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"floatright\"><a href=\"/w/File:Atlas_and_Meridian.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Atlas and Meridian.png\" src=\"/images/Atlas_and_Meridian.png?d153d\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"248\" height=\"168\" data-file-width=\"248\" data-file-height=\"168\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>Atlas and Meridian</b> are the names of the two small lizard creatures that surround the <a href=\"/w/Minimap\" title=\"Minimap\">minimap</a> on the user <a href=\"/w/Interface\" title=\"Interface\">interface</a> in fixed screen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> Their identities were revealed in the seventh issue of <a href=\"/w/Postbag_from_the_Hedge\" title=\"Postbag from the Hedge\">Postbag from the Hedge</a>. Atlas and Meridian, according to the Postbag, saw a job advertisement in the <a href=\"/w/Varrock_Herald\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Varrock Herald\">Varrock Herald</a> reading, 'Amazing opportunity for 2 trustworthy beings. Be gazed upon by millions and hold the world in your claws! No previous experience required, but good sense of direction a bonus.' The reality of their job was not what they had expected.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Atlas_and_Meridian?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Atlas_and_Meridian?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>In geography, the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meridian_(geography)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Meridian (geography)\">meridian</a> is an imaginary line that runs from the North to the South Pole. It is also an astronomical term, referring to an imaginary circle in the celestial sphere. An atlas is a collection of maps, usually placed in a book. Also, in real-world Greek mythology, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atlas_(mythology)\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Atlas (mythology)\">Atlas</a> was a titan condemned to literally hold the sky on his shoulders, while in <i>RuneScape</i>, Atlas must, in a way, hold the world up.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Atlas_and_Meridian?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Atlas_and_Meridian?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small hideQuotes\"><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Jagex. Postbag 7 - \"<a href=\"/w/Transcript:May_Mixup!#Letter_1\" title=\"Transcript:May Mixup!\">Transcript:May Mixup!</a>\", Letter 1, by Atlas and Meridian. <i>Old School RuneScape</i> Postbags from the Hedge. </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Postbag from the Hedge\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\